/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 592.0 Tm (Phantom islands endured because cartography trusted its own past. A feature once printed) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 578.0 Tm (carried an authority that absence could not easily counter, and only the slow weight of) Tj
